-Chi Liu","target":"Author/Shan-Chi Liu","line":107},{"title":"Author/Shan-Chi Liu","target":"Author/Shan-Chi Liu","line":108},{"title":"Author/Chun-Hao Tsai","target":"Author/Chun-Hao Tsai","line":109},{"title":"Author/Chun-Hao Tsai","target":"Author/Chun-Hao Tsai","line":110},{"title":"Author/Wei-Chien Huang","target":"Author/Wei-Chien Huang","line":111},{"title":"Author/Wei Chien Huang","target":"Author/Wei Chien Huang","line":112},{"title":"Author/Yang-Chang Wu","target":"Author/Yang-Chang Wu","line":113},{"title":"Author/Yang-Chang Wu","target":"Author/Yang-Chang Wu","line":114},{"title":"Author/Chih-Hsin Tang","target":"Author/Chih-Hsin Tang","line":115},{"title":"Author/Chih-Hsin Tang","target":"Author/Chih-Hsin Tang","line":116},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/yang_hericium_2022/yang_hericium_2022.pdf","line":118}],"metadata":{"id":"yang_hericium_2022","type":"article-journal","title":"Hericium erinaceus Mycelium Ameliorates In Vivo Progression of Osteoarthritis","issued":{"date-parts":[[2022]]},"DOI":"10.3390/nu14132605","container-title":"Nutrients","abstract":"Osteoarthritis (OA) is an age-related disorder that affects the joints and causes functional disability. Hericium erinaceus is a large edible mushroom with several known medicinal functions. However, the therapeutic effects of H. erinaceus in OA are unknown. In this study, data from Sprague-Dawley rats with knee OA induced by anterior cruciate ligament transection (ACLT) indicated that H. erinaceus mycelium improves ACLT-induced weight-bearing asymmetry and minimizes pain. ACLT-induced increases in articular cartilage degradation and bone erosion were significantly reduced by treatment with H. erinaceus mycelium. In addition, H. erinaceus mycelium reduced the synthesis of proinflammatory cytokines interleukin-1β and tumor necrosis factor-α in OA cartilage and synovium. H. erinaceus mycelium shows promise as a functional food in the treatment of OA.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Yang","given":"Shih Neng","literal":""},{"family":"Yang","given":"Shang-Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Fang","given":"Chi-Jung","literal":""},{"family":"Fang","given":"Chi-Jung","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yu-Wen","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Yu-Wen","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Wanping","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Wan-Ping","literal":""},{"family":"Lee","given":"Li-Ya","literal":""},{"family":"Lee","given":"Li-Ya","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chin-Chu","literal":""},{"family":"Chen","given":"Chin-Chu","literal":""},{"family":"Lin","given":"Yen-You","literal":""},{"family":"Lin","given":"Yen-You","literal":""},{"family":"Liu","given":"Shan-Chi","literal":""},{"family":"Liu","given":"Shan-Chi","literal":""},{"family":"Tsai","given":"Chun-Hao","literal":""},{"family":"Tsai","given":"Chun-Hao","literal":""},{"family":"Huang","given":"Wei-Chien","literal":""},{"family":"Huang","given":"Wei Chien","literal":""},{"family":"Wu","given":"Yang-Chang","literal":""},{"family":"Wu","given":"Yang-Chang","literal":""},{"family":"Tang","given":"Chih-Hsin","literal":""},{"family":"Tang","given":"Chih-Hsin","literal":""}],"citation-key":"yang_hericium_2022","year":"2022","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Hericium erinaceus Mycelium Ameliorates In Vivo Progression of Osteoarthritis"],"author-links":["[[Author/Shih Neng Yang]]","[[Author/Shang-Yu Yang]]","[[Author/Chi-Jung Fang]]","[[Author/Chi-Jung Fang]]","[[Author/Yu-Wen Chen]]","[[Author/Yu-Wen Chen]]","[[Author/Wanping Chen]]","[[Author/Wan-Ping Chen]]","[[Author/Li-Ya Lee]]","[[Author/Li-Ya Lee]]","[[Author/Chin-Chu Chen]]","[[Author/Chin-Chu Chen]]","[[Author/Yen-You Lin]]","[[Author/Yen-You Lin]]","[[Author/Shan-Chi Liu]]","[[Author/Shan-Chi Liu]]","[[Author/Chun-Hao Tsai]]","[[Author/Chun-Hao Tsai]]","[[Author/Wei-Chien Huang]]","[[Author/Wei Chien Huang]]","[[Author/Yang-Chang Wu]]","[[Author/Yang-Chang Wu]]","[[Author/Chih-Hsin Tang]]","[[